Package: Omixer
Type: Package
Title: Randomize Samples for -omics Profiling
Version: 0.99.3
Authors@R: person("Lucy", "Sinke", 
    email="l.j.sinke@lumc.nl", role=c("cre", "aut"))
Description: Omixer - an R package for multivariate and reproducible 
    randomization with lab-friendly sample layouts. Omixer ensures optimal 
    sample distribution across batches with well-documented methods, and 
    can output intuitive sample sheets for the wet lab if needed. 
